data.name: POST UR Song of the day

data.message:
Guys, so here is the first cut of the queued player I was discussing the other day. This creates a playlist of the songs posted here. I am going to change the script to provide finer control - Most Liked Songs, Latest Entries, etc. But that will come a while later.

Do have a look : http://prince-mishra.github.io/MyTunes

Also, to those interested in code, it is available here : https://github.com/prince-mishra/MyTunes (It is released under MIT license, so feel free to use)

I used a separate scrapper script to get content from this group and parsed it to fetch video tags, etc. This is very crude and far from completion. However this will get better in due course of time.

Suggestions/Bug reports are welcome : https://github.com/prince-mishra/MyTunes/issues

Thanks!
